<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('partials/landing/head', {
    pageTitle: 'Refund Policy – Qwint Caption by Qwintsoft LLP',
    pageDescription: '30-day money-back guarantee for Qwint Caption. Learn how to request a refund.',
    robots: 'noindex, follow',
    extraCssPath: '/assets/css/landing-pages.css'
}) %>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/landing/navbar') %>

        <main class="subpage-main">
            <div class="subpage-wrap">
                <article class="subpage-card legal-page">
                    <a href="/" class="legal-back">← Back to Home</a>
                    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
                    <p class="legal-date">Last updated: February 19, 2025</p>

                    <div class="guarantee-box" role="note" aria-label="30-day money-back guarantee">
                        <div class="guarantee-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h3>
                            <p>We stand behind Qwint Caption. If you're not fully satisfied within 30 days of purchase
                                for
                                any reason we'll refund you in full. No questions asked.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2>1. Eligibility for Refund</h2>
                    <p>You are eligible for a full refund if:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You request the refund within <strong>30 days</strong> of your original purchase date</li>
                        <li>You have not consumed more than <strong>20 credits</strong> (20 minutes of AI processing)
                        </li>
                        <li>The Software does not function as advertised on a supported system</li>
                        <li>You are unable to activate the plugin due to a verified technical issue on our end</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>2. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
                    <p>The following are not eligible for refund:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Credit top-up purchases (once purchased, credits are non-refundable)</li>
                        <li>Licenses purchased more than 30 days ago</li>
                        <li>Licenses where more than 20 credits have been consumed</li>
                        <li>Refund requests based on incompatibility with unsupported software versions or operating
                            systems
                        </li>
                        <li>Purchases made by third parties without proper authorization</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
                    <p>To request a refund, please contact our support team with the following information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your full name and email address used at purchase</li>
                        <li>Your Razorpay transaction/order ID (found in your receipt email)</li>
                        <li>Reason for refund request</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Send your refund request to: <a href="mailto:refunds@qwintsoft.com"
                            style="color:var(--clr-primary)">refunds@qwintsoft.com</a></p>
                    <p>We will respond within <strong>2 business days</strong> and process approved refunds within
                        <strong>5–10 business days</strong> via the original payment method.
                    </p>

                    <h2>4. Technical Issues</h2>
                    <p>If you experience technical issues with the Software, we strongly encourage you to contact our
                        support team <strong>before</strong> requesting a refund. Many issues can be resolved quickly,
                        and
                        we want to ensure you get the full value of your purchase. See our <a href="/support"
                            style="color:var(--clr-primary)">Support page</a> for contact options.</p>

                    <h2>5. Chargebacks</h2>
                    <p>Initiating a chargeback with your bank or card issuer without first contacting us for a refund
                        may
                        result in suspension of your license. We encourage customers to contact us directly we are
                        committed to making things right.</p>

                    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>Qwintsoft LLP reserves the right to modify this Refund Policy at any time. Changes will be posted
                        on
                        this page with an updated date. Refund requests will be handled under the policy in effect at
                        the
                        time of purchase.</p>

                    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
                    <p>Questions about refunds? We're here to help:<br />
                        <strong>Qwintsoft LLP</strong><br />
                        Email: <a href="mailto:refunds@qwintsoft.com"
                            style="color:var(--clr-primary)">refunds@qwintsoft.com</a><br />
                        Response time: within 2 business days
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/landing/footer') %>
        <script src="/assets/js/landing.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
